  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Conflict</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you will take on the role of different commanders, traversing various environments such as forests, volcanoes, and deserts. You must wisely use resources, gather allies, upgrade technology, defeat endless waves of enemies, and destroy enemy defenses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Random Battles:</strong> Various commanders and maps offer different game characteristics, making each game a new challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras/42151453844904055c33490a41c14531.avif?t=1732112001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras_big/42151453844904055c33490a41c14531.avif?t=1732112001 width=800 height=360 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras/10ceff81adc9699c6c5cf96286f409b7.avif?t=1732112001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras_big/10ceff81adc9699c6c5cf96286f409b7.avif?t=1732112001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unit and Technology Upgrades:</strong> Choose from a variety of units and use resources to upgrade randomly appearing technologies to enhance your combat power.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras/fd6dba669bb394b934986be1b49f7c13.avif?t=1732112001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras_big/fd6dba669bb394b934986be1b49f7c13.avif?t=1732112001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras/5cd7664ef24b5c738bd49a17953499fa.avif?t=1732112001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras_big/5cd7664ef24b5c738bd49a17953499fa.avif?t=1732112001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skill System:</strong> Utilize randomly dropped skills from treasure chests on the battlefield to turn the tide of battle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras/55854ff1f1ce5bdf242e91e6e5af5c53.avif?t=1732112001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras_big/55854ff1f1ce5bdf242e91e6e5af5c53.avif?t=1732112001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Item Drops:</strong> A rich item drop system allows you to obtain various useful items during battles, enhancing your combat experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras/b191596a431e9177caaf3dd1083f686c.avif?t=1732112001\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245020/extras_big/b191596a431e9177caaf3dd1083f686c.avif?t=1732112001 width=800 height=360 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to take on the challenge? Join <strong>Endless Conflict</strong> now and become the strongest commander.</p>",
